*ibam-0.5.2-r3 (23 Jan 2012)

  23 Jan 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +ibam-0.5.2-r3.ebuild,
  +files/ibam-0.5.2-build.patch:
  Fix sysfs detection problems (by migrating to Debian patchset) wrt #359891 by
  Naohiro Aota

*ibam-0.5.2-r2 (20 Mar 2011)

  20 Mar 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> +ibam-0.5.2-r2.ebuild,
  +files/ibam-0.5.2-acpi.patch:
  Make ibam working with newer kernels. Fixes bug #346811. Thanks to Simeon
  Maryasin <marsoft@ya.ru> for providing the patch.

*ibam-0.5.2-r1 (19 Oct 2010)

  19 Oct 2010; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +ibam-0.5.2-r1.ebuild,
  +files/ibam-0.5.2-ldflags.patch:
  Instill LDFLAGS respect into build system. Port to EAPI=2. Closes bug
  #341479 by Diego Elio "Flameeyes" Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>.

